data.description: Stunning Price Reduction and Views: Gorgeous Luxury Penthouse with spectacular views from every room: Golden Gate Bridge, San Francisco Bay, Alcatraz Island and beyond. Located on the northeast corner of the 39th floor of the Four Seasons 5-Star Hotel; designed and remodeled by award winning architect Andrew Skurman for the best of city living and entertaining.  PH2CD lives as one unit with two separate entrances for privacy and flexibility.  Views from every window accompany three beautiful bedrooms all with ensuite baths plus a den, chef's kitchen, formal dining room, living room, office, butler's pantry, custom cabinetry, 2 Eco-Smart e-nrg fireplaces, and powder room.   Four Seasons residents enjoy first class amenities: 24/7 concierge, doorman, room service,   security, residents only elevator, housekeeping, restaurant, bar, Equinox fitness center and spa. Deeded 2 car parking, valet available and onsite storage space.  (Dining room chandelier, dining room sconces and entryway chandelier are exceptions to the sale.)
